"    Email",
"   </a>",
"  </div>",
" </div>",
" <div class=\"graphic\">",
"  <div class=\"figure\" style=\"width: 470px\">",
"   <div class=\"ttl\">",
"    Pyogenic granuloma",
"   </div>",
"   <div class=\"cntnt\" style=\"width: 432px; height: 325px; background-image: url(data:image/jpeg;base64,);\">",
"   </div>",
"   <div class=\"lgnd\">",
"    A red, protruding vascular papule consistent with a pyogenic granuloma is present on the chest.",
"    <div class=\"footnotes\">",
"    </div>",
"    <div class=\"reference\">",
"     Reproduced with permission from: www.visualdx.com. Copyright Logical Images, Inc.",
"    </div>",
"   </div>",
"  </div>",
" </div>",
" <div class=\"graphic\">",
"  <div class=\"figure\" style=\"width: 470px\">",
"   <div class=\"ttl\">",
"    Pyogenic granuloma on the finger",
"   </div>",
"   <div class=\"cntnt\" style=\"width: 420px; height: 273px; background-image: url(data:image/jpeg;base64,);\">",
"   </div>",
"   <div class=\"lgnd\">",
"    A rapidly growing, red, dome-shaped, friable papule with a collarette of scale is consistent with a pyogenic granuloma.",
"    <div class=\"footnotes\">",
